{"tid":2408744,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"有咩on9得過將元朗721恐怖襲擊整成線上遊戲？","createTime":"2021-02-15T08:31:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T16:39:58.000Z","uid":307619,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"97858f652abe5b1433d6a6482d0b2d732e38df8c","tid":2408744,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T08:31:07.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">就係竟然有人on9到眾籌支持阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n//重現元朗 7.21 白衣人襲擊　遊戲《曼陀羅的傳承》 <span class=\"red\">眾籌達標</span><br />\n<br />\n香港一名大學生早前受 7.21 元朗恐襲啟發，自學製作的遊戲《曼陀羅的傳承》，<span class=\"red\">他發起眾籌 10 萬元以支持整個遊戲的製作，今日眾籌正式達標。</span><br />\n<br />\n大學四年級生 Mighcty 自學製作 2D 像素風角色扮演遊戲 &mdash; 遊戲《曼陀羅的傳承》。<span class=\"red\">遊戲主角回家途中在車站目擊市民被大量身穿白衣、手持武器的男子攻擊，所以使用法術拯救乘客 。</span>遊戲早前在 Kickstarter 進行眾籌，目標金額為 10 萬港元。眾籌進入最後 8 小時之際，項目終於達標。<br />\n<br />\n《曼陀羅的傳承》不乏香港抗爭元素，包括：<span class=\"red\">恐襲下的元朗站</span>、將軍澳連儂隧道、學生人鏈等。Mighcty 接受《立場新聞》訪問時表示，起初只計劃做一隻遊戲介紹香港，但 7.21 事件令他對政府撤底失望，故置入多項時事元素。<br />\n<br />\nMighcty 現已完成《曼陀羅的傳承》的試玩版本，並獲外國玩家拍下實測影片。<span class=\"red\">有玩家分不清真假</span>，留言問遊戲內容是否真有其事，他回應稱「兩者都十分荒謬，你見到一大班白衣人出現﹐而冇警察到場，《變型金剛》嘅情節先會出現㗎啫。」<br />\n<br />\n網上找教材自學製作遊戲的 Mighcty 曾言，眾籌成功的話會用一兩年時間全職開發遊戲，<span class=\"red\">「希望可以做到一隻高質的遊戲畀全世界享受」</span>。//<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZuTx8Dx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZuTx8Dx.png&h=86b7aa70&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d5728d29e70d4d45a9c5de324997534249e790e8","tid":2408744,"uid":64337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T08:31:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b42909d068fcde309fc92b7b49723649cfccd79","tid":2408744,"uid":246371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T08:32:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf7ff6367b67eb17a28be032822026214419aa40","tid":2408744,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T08:32:59.000Z","msg":"黨鐵7.21 de Go!"},{"pid":"e1bd5594fc49fa52edc304b42da08f4ad182a50f","tid":2408744,"uid":86509,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T08:34:17.000Z","msg":"文宣嚟啫<br />\n真係考驗遊戲製作者能力<br />\n其實文字圖畫任何藝術都只係訊息嘅載體<br />\n遊戲就真係比較難去做<br />\n希望手足有呢個功力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nanyway做得幾好都一定有人唔滿意"},{"pid":"46bd56573808b92dcdf0d78e72717703862a6585","tid":2408744,"uid":23170,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T08:35:03.000Z","msg":"件事又未到on9嘅，但foresee到成品應該會好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40922184358300f0aae81a446761454ce098e9e7","tid":2408744,"uid":121546,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T08:37:17.000Z","msg":"比較想玩columbine high school shooting既遊戲"},{"pid":"10496db9f6627c6990e07cfabfed48f32a1da139","tid":2408744,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"46bd56573808b92dcdf0d78e72717703862a6585","tid":2408744,"uid":23170,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T08:35:03.000Z","msg":"件事又未到on9嘅，但foresee到成品應該會好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T08:37:28.000Z","msg":"其實用恐怖元素<br />\n做到返校咁<br />\n會好做啲"},{"pid":"4a48539dbe265168448398362880c3d630236933","tid":2408744,"uid":13745,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T08:52:40.000Z","msg":"64應該都可以出game 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支聯會幾時出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />